;        that ran. form-macho's wrap is ABI-agnostic; in-kernel float-call later wants a small dylib_call_f64ptr.
;     C. ✓ DONE — weight-load.fk (4095): gguf-locate + wl-slice + f16-decode + q6k-dequant load a REAL
