;        fcos, bin power is the Goertzel recurrence, a mel row is its slaney (bins, weights) support as
;        data, log10 is trig.fk's new fln. Matches torch.stft frame 5 / librosa slaney / whisper's
;        clamp-log lane at 1e-6 — but 3-KERNEL ONLY (mel-frame is not in form/fourth-arm-bands.txt; the
;        fourth-arm gap is host-io / node-family ops not yet on the walker). The full 80×3000 spectrogram
;        is this recipe walked — speed is M5's JIT stone, not a new shape. Remaining for M6: safetensors
;        carrier + block-0 activation match — and the reference teacher is now a LOCAL oracle on this host
;        (whisper.cpp / whisper-cli, on-device, Metal+BLAS), not a cloud HF pull. See oracle-catalog.fk.]
;        [FORWARD-PASS EXTENSION SHIPPED: the whole whisper-tiny ARCHITECTURE now runs in Form, each piece
;        proven against the numpy/fp64 reference at tiny dims — multi-head self-attention + encoder stack
;        (transformer-mh.fk, max|Δ| 4e-16 over a 4-layer stack); the decoder block — causal masked
;        self-attention + cross-attention + FFN + stack (transformer-decoder.fk, max|Δ| 2e-16, and the
;        causal mask proven genuinely causal: a future token moves position-0 output by exactly 0.0); and
;        the greedy autoregressive loop — embed+positional → decoder → layernorm_post → tied-embedding
;        logits → argmax → feed back (transformer-generate.fk, EXACT token-id-sequence parity). Bands:
;        tests/transformer-{mh,decoder,generate}-band.fk, three-way (the fkwu float-band gap is the same
;        named host-io/node-family limitation as mel-frame). Remaining to a real transcript: real
;        d_model=384 weights via M5's JIT, conv stem + full 80×3000 mel, sinusoidal/learned positionals,
;        BPE tokenizer.]
;        [REAL-WEIGHT + FRONT-END + TOKENIZER RUNGS SHIPPED: (1) REAL openai/whisper-tiny encoder
;        block-0 weights (offline from the HF cache), REAL 6-head multi-head, run through tb-mh-block —
;        at d_model=96 max|Form-numpy(tanh-gelu)|=3e-16, and at FULL d_model=384/head_dim=64 = 6.66e-15
;        in 33.6s (a 34.6MB literal-emit program — it RUNS and is bit-right at full width; throughput for
;        a whole 8-layer/1500-pos model is M5's JIT, not correctness). The only residual vs whisper's true
;        output is erf-gelu vs the body's tanh-gelu (~4e-3) — the named M3 follow-up. scripts/
